and me from here on out.

107
00:06:49,248 --> 00:06:50,822
Partners.

108
00:06:52,917 --> 00:06:55,910
- You mean, like Batman and Robin?
- Yeah.

109
00:06:56,585 --> 00:06:58,460
Like Batman and Robin.

110
00:07:00,177 --> 00:07:01,292
Only...

111
00:07:02,425 --> 00:07:04,250
I  ain't wearing no tights.

