114
00:07:37,908 --> 00:07:39,202
Micah!

115
00:07:40,298 --> 00:07:43,221
Did you ever consider that these
dreams that you've been having,

116
00:07:43,256 --> 00:07:45,350
- are just that, dreams?
- It's impossible.

117
00:07:45,676 --> 00:07:49,173
They were talking about my sister
Shanti, a sister I never knew I had!

118
00:07:49,427 --> 00:07:51,523
As children,
we absorb powerful archetypes

119
00:07:51,686 --> 00:07:53,341
