He was one of them,
right here in Chennai.

125
00:08:08,367 --> 00:08:11,283
Sanjog Iyer,
my father identified the genetic marker.

126
00:08:11,535 --> 00:08:13,432
It says the boy can
enter your dreams,

127
00:08:13,616 --> 00:08:16,332
alter your perceptions,
uh,  kind of spirit guide.

128
00:08:16,538 --> 00:08:19,971
- You must have seen that file before.
- I have never seen this file before,

129
00:08:20,005 --> 00:08:22,302
and I have had thousands
of dreams in my life.

130
00:08:22,377 --> 00:08:24,640
These were different, they were...
they were real.

131
00:08:24,678 --> 00:08:26,751
We have to find this boy.

132
00:08:29,428 --> 00:08:32,720
Hey, what was so important
you had me meet you over here?

133
00:08:33,015 --> 00:08:35,913
That painting you wanted,
Nathan bought it from Linderman,

134
00:08:36,146 --> 00:08:38,642
- had it shipped here.
- It's here... Can I see it?

135
00:08:39,725 --> 00:08:41,183
There.

136
00:08:45,908 --> 00:08:49,270
I-I don't understand.

137
00:08:49,535 --> 00:08:51,031
He said it was to protect you,

138
00:08:51,037 --> 00:08:53,071
that you're gonna
get yourself killed.

139
00:08:54,536 --> 00:08:55,663
Okay, wait a minute.

140
00:08:56,075 --> 00:08:57,723
You saw this painting,
all right.

141
00:08:58,087 --> 00:09:00,423
- You can describe it to me.
- You really believe this, don't you?

142
00:09:00,457 --> 00:09:02,130
Save the cheerleader,
save the world.

143
00:09:02,165 --> 00:09:04,460
For reasons I can't
begin to understand...

144
00:09:04,711 --> 00:09:07,381
There are people that are
counting on me to do this.

145
00:09:07,714 --> 00:09:11,051
I don't know if I can,
but I have to try.

146
00:09:20,933 --> 00:09:22,850
This doesn't make any sense.

147
00:09:24,899 --> 00:09:28,192
I probably shouldn't
be showing you this.

148
00:09:29,488 --> 00:09:32,613
It's a digital image,
it came with the painting.

149
00:09:33,947 --> 00:09:36,360
Is that you, Peter?

150
00:09:37,615 --> 00:09:41,542
I...I don't know.

151
00:09:43,128 --> 00:09:44,501
Maybe.

152
00:09:46,587 --> 00:09:52,133
If it's you,
then you're gonna die at 8:12 tonight.

153
00:09:55,138 --> 00:09:57,340
- Don't go, Peter.
- I have to.

154
00:09:58,348 --> 00:10:00,552
I have to.

155
00:10:04,475 --> 00:10:07,103
Union Wells High School
is in Odessa, Texas.

156
00:10:07,148 --> 00:10:09,190
I took the liberty
and made a phone call.

157
00:10:09,565 --> 00:10:11,361
Homecoming is tonight.

158
00:10:14,616 --> 00:10:17,572
Thank you. Thank you.

159
00:10:18,246 --> 00:10:20,390
Look,  I don't know if
this is gonna happen.

160
00:10:20,667 --> 00:10:22,993
- Just come back, okay?
- I will.

161
00:10:47,856 --> 00:10:49,441
Hiro? Hiro!

162
