Hi, this is Peter Petrelli,
is this Hiro Nakamura?

163
00:10:52,367 --> 00:10:55,983
- No. Ah, he will be right back.
- Who is this?

164
00:10:56,197 --> 00:10:58,861
- I'm his friend, Ando.
- Ando, right.

165
00:10:59,157 --> 00:11:01,952
Okay, this is very important.

166
00:11:02,208 --> 00:11:05,492
