Texas, as soon as you can...

167
00:11:05,708 --> 00:11:07,251
Union Wells High School.

168
00:11:07,506 --> 00:11:09,132
Okay, that's where
the cheerleader is.

169
00:11:09,165 --> 00:11:10,542
