172
00:11:16,557 --> 00:11:18,253
Listen, I'm gonna
get on a flight,

173
00:11:18,385 --> 00:11:20,652
tell Hiro that I'll be
there before he knows it.

174
00:11:20,686 --> 00:11:22,932
Yes, okay. I will tell him.

175
00:11:23,105 --> 00:11:25,100
Good-bye, Peter Petrelli.

176
00:11:31,275 --> 00:11:33,773
It's gonna be okay, honey.

177
00:11:56,468 --> 00:11:57,880
