impairing your judgment.

183
00:12:11,646 --> 00:12:14,063
Maybe, but I'm
not the only one.

184
00:12:14,316 --> 00:12:17,440
When he wakes up,
have him paint another.

185
00:12:18,907 --> 00:12:20,151
No.

186
00:12:22,866 --> 00:12:24,991
You think I'm being emotional?

187
00:12:25,286 --> 00:12:27,530
Do you have any idea
what we're up against?

188
00:12:28,297 --> 00:12:29,583
Come here.

189
00:12:33,295 --> 00:12:34,501
Oh, my God.

190
00:12:36,007 --> 00:12:38,591
