Wait for Sylar.

196
00:13:00,077 --> 00:13:01,651
You'll have help.

197
00:13:01,948 --> 00:13:03,991
When the time is right,
neutralize him.

198
00:13:04,366 --> 00:13:07,742
- I'll keep Claire safe at home.
- No, it's homecoming.

199
00:13:07,996 --> 00:13:10,542
Find Sylar, take him out.

200
00:13:10,836 --> 00:13:13,620
And let me worry about Claire.

201
00:13:22,218 --> 00:13:25,512
- Congratulations, Claire.
- Thanks so much!

202
00:13:25,847 --> 00:13:27,432
I don't know that girl.

203
00:13:27,768 --> 00:13:31,012
- Holla to the queen!
- Holla back!

204
