Look, everybody who's like
Jackie voted for Jackie,

211
00:13:46,827 --> 00:13:48,723
and everybody who
isn't voted for you.

212
00:13:48,746 --> 00:13:51,891
And in this school, the unpopular
vastly outnumber the popular.

213
00:13:52,046 --> 00:13:54,082
