of your old life back, okay?

220
00:14:14,356 --> 00:14:17,230
Just don't start acting
like a bitch again.

221
00:14:17,486 --> 00:14:20,193
Look, I got this
off of the Internet.

222
00:14:20,526 --> 00:14:24,112
