but I could be nicer.

228
00:14:44,135 --> 00:14:46,053
Then why don't you?

229
00:14:47,675 --> 00:14:50,091
Congratulations, Claire.

230
00:14:50,595 --> 00:14:53,182
Mmm, is the gay boy your date?

231
